<div class="log">
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▷&nbsp;行动：乳糖不耐&nbsp;◁</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">△&nbsp;代号：乳房如何半衰&nbsp;△</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content"></div>
